description:
The course is about periodic table. By this course you can learn Classification of elements and periodicity in properties,

The p-block elements 15th group,

The p-block elements 16th group,

The p-block elements 17th group

The p-block elements 18th group and

The d and f-block elements

This course can be completed in a month.

The course is of 50+ videos of concepts covering above topics.

The course is made of full 3d digital videos with animations, so you can learn the topiics very easily,
title: Periodic Table Part - 2
